title: AIMS, Afghanistan Lakes, Afghanistan, 2004
name: AIMS, Afghanistan Lakes, Afghanistan, 2004
description:
Abstract:
        Lakes depicts lake polygon features from United States Defense Mapping Agency (USDMA) 1:100,000 scale topo maps. This layer includes both major and minor lakes. 
    Purpose:
        Lakes is a base map layer of polygon lakes features mapped at a 1:100,000 scale. Users must assume responsibility in determining the useability of this data for their purpose. Data at this scale is suitable for general studies and local planning.
